reviewText: Received quickly and reasonably priced.  Have not yet had a chance to watch the movies; but, I'm sure they are as I remember them.
It's alright, nothing to write home about.
Good price for 6 movies, so if you like even two of them it is a good buy. I rated it as a two because only two of them were worth the price of admission in my personal opinion.
These were ok but I didn't cry in any of them. They weren't emotional enough for me. I like ones with emotional and animal stories.
These weren't real tear jerker a, not like Nicholas Sparks movies, but okay anyway.
I bought this movie for Avalon which I had seen before and love this movie, however I did not like any of the other movies on this DVD.
Good sad chick flick movies.  Enjoyed.
My Life and To Gillian on her 32 birthday are well worth the price of this DVD. Both truly are great tear jerkers!
One of the DVDs was cracked and I e-mailed the company without any results. The other DVD was fine.
Would have been better if movies had captions or subtitles in english.  Ok .....
CRAP old, really old movies. Sent back
very nice dvd set  good movies  seller rates well  delivery on time  thanks
